{"tid":2044011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［還治其人之身］美國黑暴係有人出錢請佢地搞事！","createTime":"2020-05-30T20:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T23:57:04.000Z","uid":205394,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62d6e0edddae47128cf99bc0add02d4c37414311","tid":2044011,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:44:09.000Z","msg":"無錯！<br />\n香港班示威者擺到明係收左美國佬錢先搞事<br />\n呢個已經係公開既秘密，人人都知架啦！<br />\n就算無收錢，都係被收左美國佬錢果班煽動佢地先去搞事！<br />\n<br />\n美國佬做到既野我地中國都做到！<br />\n我地偉大既中國美德係<br />\n人不犯我 我不犯人，人若犯我 雖遠必誅！<br />\n<br />\n你地出錢請人搞事好叻咩？<br />\n美國今次既黑暴，一定都係收左錢先做野<br />\n咁究竟係邊個出既錢呢？<br />\n哈！你知我知，大家心照啦！<br />\n你做得既野我地偉大祖國都一定做得，重會做得更好！<br />\n<br />\n今次真係心都涼埋！<br />\n以其人之道 還治其人之身！<br />\n而且好明顯美國警察無香港警察咁高效率囉！<br />\n真係好廢，有槍有武器都唔識用！"},{"pid":"c73852f1df456508390e01d98495ff512a351161","tid":2044011,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:46:08.000Z","msg":"報應囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9292b26f9f283b10f7f7c64cb6f72a1cc9a07aaf","tid":2044011,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:48:37.000Z","msg":"有人搞事就一定係有人出錢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14856f7e8c134244936bf678a4c814b6bc0826c6","tid":2044011,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:48:52.000Z","msg":"美國嬲嬲豬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258430e8ebe3412f816158337119ad7eb6483f55","tid":2044011,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed8e7553b39d3d8ce64ee82a6dd6fb1f6dc7f7a","tid":2044011,"uid":87030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:15:52.000Z","msg":"低級黑"},{"pid":"6afd611f7e5cd703af4dd8ae5bb3a66be4963ddb","tid":2044011,"uid":66507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"